Author: dacryptomoney
Title: [ANN][ICO + AIRDROP+BOUNTY] AMOR - MEET CREDIBLE PEOPLE - ICO IS NOW OPEN
Body: Our bounty has started. https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2432271  We're starting a bounty program with less than 15 days to go for our crowdsale. We've been overwhelmed with the support we've received on all our channels during the Airdrop campaign and otherwise. Not everyone could get tokens during the Airdrop campaign, however here is a last opportunity to grab some tokens before the crowdsale begins.  Spread the word around for our project and get rewarded with Amor tokens. Use your Facebook, Twitter, Redditt, BitcoinTalk profile- whatever has the highest outreach and ask everyone to buy Amor tokens. Here are few tiers in which we'll be rewarding during the bounty:   1) Retweet us on Twitter - 100 Amor 2) Post your own status on FB/ Twitter asking people to support and buy Amor, and get 1-10 likes: 300 Amor 3) Post your own status on FB/ Twitter asking people to support and buy Amor, and get 10+likes: 600 Amor 4) Post on other forums in BitcoinTalk asking people to buy Amor: 1000 Amor 5) Write a post on /r /ethTrader and get at least 10 upvotes for it- 1500 Amor   For each of these, we need evidence that you actually posted it. Here is the form https://goo.gl/forms/K3A3i1yXXazL5ft63 - put your ETH address with the evidence of your post, and results. We have lot more coins to give away for Bounty than Airdrop, so don't delay it, get started right now.  Form for entering your evidence: https://goo.gl/forms/K3A3i1yXXazL5ft63  Spreadsheet with responses: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/18_NS0pqbGkZ2FnPbPE0T3-Wrp68jhPJWztXgKKJWK-M/edit?usp=sharing  Here is a sample in case you're wondering what to post:   "Amor Coin is looking to revolutionize the dating industry by bringing credibility with the use of blockchain. Find out more about them at amorcoin.org and make sure to take part in their crowdsale starting 2nd December"  We look forward to another big participation. Don't miss out on your last chance before the crowdsale.
